01:20:26.572 --> 01:20:27.932
The only way to
survive in Hamburg,

01:20:28.157 --> 01:20:29.277
to play eight hours a night,

01:20:29.492 --> 01:20:31.303
was to take pills, like
the waiters gave you it.

01:20:31.327 --> 01:20:32.453
Pills and a drink.

