01:25:47.309 --> 01:25:48.869
a little bit of the
rock and roll stuff,

01:25:48.978 --> 01:25:50.521
I've always felt that.

01:25:50.771 --> 01:25:52.982
But the point is, you
can't argue with the fact,

01:25:53.232 --> 01:25:54.232
it worked.

01:25:55.234 --> 01:25:56.819
We were four guys that,

01:25:57.069 --> 01:25:58.964
I met Paul, and said do
you want to join my band?

01:25:58.988 --> 01:26:02.116
You know, and then
George joined,

01:26:02.366 --> 01:26:03.927
and then Ringo joined,
we were just a band

01:26:03.951 --> 01:26:06.662
who made it very,
very big, that's all.

01:26:06.912 --> 01:26:09.248
