recorded, you know.

01:26:09.498 --> 01:26:11.834
In Liverpool, Hamburg,
and around the dance halls, you know?

01:26:12.084 --> 01:26:15.129
And what we generated
was fantastic,

01:26:15.379 --> 01:26:17.298
where we played straight rock,

01:26:17.548 --> 01:26:19.884
and there was nobody
to touch us in Britain.

01:26:20.134 --> 01:26:22.428
But as soon as we
made it, we made it.

01:26:22.678 --> 01:26:25.055
The edges were knocked off.

01:26:25.306 --> 01:26:26.724
Brian put us in
suits and all that,

01:26:26.974 --> 01:26:28.174
and we made it very, very big,

01:26:28.392 --> 01:26:29.518
but we sold out.

01:26:29.768 --> 01:26:31.478
And the music was
dead before we even

01:26:31.729 --> 01:26:33.439
went on the theater
tour of Britain.

01:26:35.566 --> 01:26:37.026
We were feeling shit already.

01:26:38.402 --> 01:26:39.588
The Beatles made it

01:26:39.612 --> 01:26:40.946
